Jan 2024 • Couples
Majestic Place no matter what day/night cruise ship you decide to take. But if you're wanting to avoid crowds at the main tourist spots like Titov island etc you have to go before 12pm otherwise your gonna just be with every other tour group. Unless your group reaches there before the others you'll spend an hour in queues. You can't see anything at night as there's no lights on the islands so spending the night makes little difference.
